 are in Prague, said Babis|website=Mlad\u00e1 fronta DNES|language=cs |access-date=12 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''96'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Liberec Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Regional Hospital Liberec}}\n| Female\n| 59\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | The first case in [[Liberec Region]] is a 59-year-old woman who was skiing in Italy. She had symptoms and stayed home after she told her employer, she moved to hospital on 10 March. Reportedly in mild condition.<ref name=\"mar12.news.idnes\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''97'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Karlovy Vary Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| 65+\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | The first case in [[Karlovy Vary Region]] is a man over 65 years old who was skiing in Italy. Mild condition.<ref name=\"mar12.news.idnes\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''98'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Prague]]\n| [[Litomy\u0161l]]\n| [[Pardubice Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Pardubice Hospital}}\n| Female\n| 30\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | The second case in [[Pardubice Region]] is a woman from Litomy\u0161l that was infected in Prague. She works in administrative and was in contact with another case, which is why she was tested. Even though she has no symptoms, regional epidemiologist said she will be transferred to Pardubice Hospital.<ref name=\"mar12.news.idnes\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''99'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Failure|Community spread}}\n| {{fl